#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!meta title=\"How can I trust Tails?\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!meta title=\"Com puc confiar en Tails?\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!meta stylesheet=\"donate/testimonials.inline\" rel=\"stylesheet\" title=\"\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!meta stylesheet=\"donate/testimonials.inline\" rel=\"stylesheet\" title=\"\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Tails will never try to harm you or any of our users, as a core principle of "
"our [[Social Contract|about/social_contract]]. As part of that commitment, "
"we have written this page to help you make an informed decision about "
"whether you can trust Tails."
msgstr ""
"Tails mai intentarà fer-vos mal ni a cap dels nostres usuaris, com a "
"principi bàsic del nostre [[Contracte Social|about/social_contract]]. Com a "
"part d'aquest compromís, hem escrit aquesta pàgina per ajudar-vos a prendre "
"una decisió informada sobre si podeu confiar en Tails."

#. type: Plain text
msgid "We think that Tails is a trustworthy project because:"
msgstr "Creiem que Tails és un projecte de confiança perquè:"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "- **Our work is public**"
msgstr "- **El nostre treball és públic**"

#. type: Bullet: '  - '
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Tails is [[Free Software|about/license]] and security researchers can "
#| "examine our [[!tails_gitlab desc=\"source code\"]]."
msgid ""
"Tails is [[Free Software|about/license]] and security researchers can "
"examine our [[!tails_gitlab tails/tails desc=\"source code\"]]."
msgstr ""
"Tails és [[Programari Lliure|about/license]] i investigadors de seguretat "
"poden examinar el nostre [[!tails_gitlab desc=\"codi font\"]]."

#. type: Bullet: '  - '
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Known issues in Tails are described publicly in our [[!tails_gitlab "
#| "desc=\"GitLab issue tracker\"]]. We might hide embargoed security "
#| "vulnerabilities in Tails while we work on a solution, but only as a way "
#| "of protecting our users."
msgid ""
"Known issues in Tails are described publicly in our [[!tails_gitlab tails/"
"tails/-/issues desc=\"GitLab issue tracker\"]]. We might hide embargoed "
"security vulnerabilities in Tails while we work on a solution, but only as a "
"way of protecting our users."
msgstr ""
"Els problemes coneguts de Tails es descriuen públicament al nostre [[!"
"tails_gitlab desc=\"rastrejador de problemes de GitLab\"]]. Podem amagar "
"vulnerabilitats de seguretat trobades a Tails mentre treballem en una "
"solució, però només com a forma de protegir els nostres usuaris."

#. type: Bullet: '  - '
msgid ""
"The most sensitive parts of Tails are explained in our [[design documents|"
"contribute/design]]."
msgstr ""
"Les parts més sensibles de Tails s'expliquen als nostres [[documents de "
"disseny|contribute/design]]."

#. type: Plain text
msgid "- **Tails is based on Tor and Debian**"
msgstr "- **Tails es basa en Tor i Debian**"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  Most of the software included in Tails has not been written by us, but is\n"
"  inherited from Tor and Debian:\n"
msgstr ""
"  La majoria del programari inclòs a Tails no ha estat escrit per nosaltres, però sí\n"
"  heretat de Tor i Debian:\n"

#. type: Bullet: '  * '
msgid ""
"[Debian](https://debian.org/) is one of the oldest Linux distributions and "
"the one with the most derivatives, including Ubuntu. Debian and its "
"derivatives are [the most popular Linux distributions on web servers]"
"(https://w3techs.com/technologies/details/os-linux) across the Internet. The "
"Debian project is coordinated over the Internet by a team of volunteers "
"whose work is entirely public. All this makes Debian one of the Free "
"Software projects under the most scrutiny by security researchers."
msgstr ""
"[Debian](https://debian.org/) és una de les distribucions de Linux més "
"antigues i la que té més derivats, inclòs Ubuntu. Debian i els seus derivats "
"són [les distribucions de Linux més populars als servidors web](https://"
"w3techs.com/technologies/details/os-linux) a Internet. El projecte Debian "
"està coordinat a través d'Internet per un equip de voluntaris, el treball "
"dels quals és totalment públic. Tot això fa de Debian un dels projectes de "
"programari lliure més controlats pels investigadors de seguretat."

#. type: Bullet: '  * '
msgid ""
"[Tor](https://torproject.org/) is the best anonymity network available. Tor "
"has partnered with leading research institutions and has been subjected to "
"intensive academic research. Tor has received awards from institutions such "
"as the [EFF](https://www.eff.org/awards/pioneer/2012) and the [Free Software "
"Foundation](https://www.fsf.org/news/2010-free-software-awards-announced).  "
"Even the NSA qualified Tor as \"[the King of high secure, low latency "
"Internet Anonymity](https://www.theguardian.com/world/interactive/2013/"
"oct/04/tor-high-secure-internet-anonymity).\""
msgstr ""
"[Tor](https://torproject.org/) és la millor xarxa d'anonimat disponible. Tor "
"s'ha associat amb institucions de recerca líders i ha estat sotmès a una "
"intensa investigació acadèmica. Tor ha rebut premis d'institucions com "
"l'[EFF](https://www.eff.org/awards/pioneer/2012) i la [Free Software "
"Foundation](https://www.fsf.org/news/2010-free-software-awards-announced). "
"Fins i tot la NSA va qualificar Tor com \"[el rei de l'anonimat d'Internet "
"d'alta seguretat i baixa latència](https://www.theguardian.com/world/"
"interactive/2013/oct/04/tor-high-secure-internet-anonymity).\""

#. type: Plain text
msgid "- **Our downloads are verifiable**"
msgstr "- **Les nostres baixades són verificables**"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  Making sure that our users are really downloading an unmodified version of\n"
"  our work is also critical to trust and security:\n"
msgstr ""
"  Assegurar-nos que els nostres usuaris estan baixant realment una versió no modificada\n"
"  del nostre treball també és fonamental per a la confiança i la seguretat:\n"

#. type: Bullet: '  * '
msgid ""
"Our downloads are [[reproducible|contribute/build/reproducible]] to make "
"sure that the process of building the downloads from our source code was not "
"altered by our own infrastructure."
msgstr ""
"Les nostres baixades són [[reproduïbles|contribute/build/reproducible]] per "
"assegurar-nos que el procés de creació de les baixades des del nostre codi "
"font no hagi estat alterat per la nostra pròpia infraestructura."

#. type: Bullet: '  * '
msgid ""
"We provide [[strong and easy-to-use verification mechanisms|contribute/"
"design/download_verification]] to make sure that our users are downloading a "
"genuine copy of Tails."
msgstr ""
"Oferim [[mecanismes de verificació sòlids i fàcils d'utilitzar|contribute/"
"design/download_verification]] per assegurar-nos que els nostres usuaris "
"estan baixant una còpia genuïna de Tails."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"- **Tails is recommended by renown and diverse people and organizations**"
msgstr ""
"- **Tails és recomanat per persones i organitzacions reconegudes i diverses**"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "  See also our list of [[sponsors]].\n"
msgstr "  Vegeu també la nostra llista de [[patrocinadors|sponsors]].\n"

